{"id":578791,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/02/【立此存照】北京血小板危机：求助微博成负面/","date":"2018-02-17T08:46:43Z","modified":"2018-02-17T08:46:43Z","title":"【立此存照】北京血小板危机：求助微博成“负面信息”","content":"<p><strong>【编者注】</strong>在2017年北京市互助献血比例<a href=\"http://www.bjnews.com.cn/feature/2018/02/14/476417_2.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">已达21%</a>的前提下，该市卫计委于2018年2月10日紧急取消互助献血，导致血小板供应出现了<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/02/%e8%8a%b1%e7%81%ab%e7%88%b1%e4%b8%bd%e4%b8%9d-%ef%bc%9a%e5%a4%a7%e9%87%8f%e7%97%85%e4%ba%ba%e6%97%a0%e8%a1%80%e5%8f%af%e8%be%93%e6%b4%bb%e6%b4%bb%e7%ad%89%e6%ad%bb%ef%bc%8c%e8%bf%99%e6%98%af%e5%8c%97/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">严重紧缺</a>，大量高危血液病人（血小板指数个位数）无法获得血小板资源。</p>\n<p>市卫计委后来发表声明，称已从外省调剂资源，目前“血液中心血小板库存正常，供需平衡，可以满足临床需求”。<strong>但病友在社交网络<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/02/%e5%8c%97%e4%ba%ac%e8%a1%80%e5%b0%8f%e6%9d%bf%e5%8d%b1%e6%9c%ba%ef%bc%9a%e5%ae%98%e6%96%b9%e7%a7%b0%e5%ba%93%e5%ad%98%e5%85%85%e8%b6%b3%e5%b7%b2%e5%a4%96%e8%b0%83-%e7%97%85%e5%8f%8b%e7%a7%b0%e8%b5%84/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">透露出的信息</a>却是，血小板紧缺情况没有任何改善。</strong>如下图中这位用户名为 @鱼蜀黍的吉他 的微博认证用户，血小板个位数（正常值为100～300）仍无血可输：<strong><br />\n</strong></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_578803\" style=\"width: 535px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/病友1.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-578803\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/病友1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"398\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/病友1.jpg 1083w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/病友1-300x227.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/病友1-768x582.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/病友1-1024x776.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">微博截图</span></p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_578804\" style=\"width: 535px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/病友2.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-578804\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/病友2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"512\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/病友2.jpg 1082w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/病友2-300x293.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/病友2-768x750.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/病友2-1024x999.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">微博截图</span></p></div>\n<p>血小板需要去指定地点用专用仪器来采集，普通献血点无法进行，采集后冷藏有效期仅5天。北京市卫计委近日安抚民众的“外省调剂”的声明，即使是真实的，也并不适用于血小板这种有效期极短的紧缺资源。</p>\n<blockquote><p><strong>相关专题</strong>：<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/tag/%e5%8c%97%e4%ba%ac%e8%a1%80%e5%b0%8f%e6%9d%bf%e5%8d%b1%e6%9c%ba/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">北京血小板危机</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><strong>2018年2月16日，<a href=\"https://weibo.com/6416309419/G3rKDgatl\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">血小板指数只有1的白血病患者</a> @爱骑车的李子熙 想用微博推广自己的求助信息，却被告知内容涉及“不适宜推广”的“负面信息”，未通过审核。</strong></p>\n<blockquote><p><a href=\"https://weibo.com/2841616851/G3pdMBDA7\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">@爱骑车的李子熙</a>：渣浪请你要点脸谢谢[微笑]</p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/微博推广1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-578794\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/微博推广1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"866\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/微博推广1.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/微博推广1-139x300.jpg 139w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/微博推广1-473x1024.jpg 473w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>由于您的博文涉及[不适宜推广-负面信息]相关的关键词，未通过我们的广告审核，故您的该条博文不能推广给您的潜在粉丝；但并不会影响您粉丝部分的推广效果。</p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/微博推广2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-578795\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/微博推广2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"866\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/微博推广2.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/微博推广2-139x300.jpg 139w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/微博推广2-473x1024.jpg 473w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/微博推广3.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-578796\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/微博推广3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"866\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/微博推广3.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/微博推广3-139x300.jpg 139w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/微博推广3-473x1024.jpg 473w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,27949],"tags":[33986,31904,33991,10782,18810,9503,8616]}